snippet.title: I did the impossible | Rotation by DennisByDEN.
snippet.description:
Zero deaths.

A full playthrough of Rotation, an Itch.io game made by my friend DennisByDEN. Why am I so good at this? I playtested it. Did Dennis beat it? Nope. How long did it take me to master the last level? Don't even ask.

This game is playable in browser, or you can download the Windows version.
Link:
https://dennisbyden.itch.io/rotation
